Study visa checklist for Seychellois 
You will need these for your visa application to study in the UK: 

 Your passport; 
 A Confirmation of Acceptance for Studies (CAS) certificate; 
 Evidence of funds to cover your first year’s course fees and up to 9 months’ living 
costs; 
 Proof of your relationship with your parent or legal guardian if the funds are held in 
an account owned by them, and a supporting letter from them confirming you have 
permission to use this money; 
